[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "監察官",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お二方とも、お疲れさまです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_714_036_01331",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "お疲れさまです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01332",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ご苦労。経過報告を聞こう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01333",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "王妃の逮捕からしばらく経つが……\nベスティラはどうなっている？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01334",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "監察官",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はっ、当初は混乱も見られましたが、\n獣人特有の明るい性格もあり、今や平常運転です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_714_036_01335",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "獣人って、いつも前向きですもんねぇ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01336",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "うむ。国王陛下の様子はどうだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01337",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "監察官",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はい。変わりなく治政と武道会を行っています。\n以前より酒の量が増えたようではありますが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_714_036_01338",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "責任を感じているのだろう。あとは自分の目で\n確かめてみるとしよう。行くぞ、タイニー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01339",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい、ボス！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01340",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "なんか、バタバタしてますね。\n私たちの監査に慌ててるんでしょうか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01341",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "いや、違う……！　襲撃者だ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01342",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "お前、何者だ！　陛下に何をした！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01343",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "何を？　この国は力こそすべてだと言うから、\n王に対して管理者の力を見せてやったまでだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01344",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "管理者……？　もしかして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01345",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺の宣言を受けて、先に手を出したのは王のほうだ。\nまったく、この国は思い上がっているな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01346",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "だからこそ……俺が「管理」してやるのも\nやぶさかではない、かな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01347",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "その大上段からの物言い……そうか、お前は\nパルメ族、もしくはその遣いの九偉人だな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01348",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "人間の罪は同じ人間が裁く！\n人間の事情に口を挟むな！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01349",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺たちのことを知っている……\nそうか、お前らもあの錬金術士の仲間か",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01350",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "あれだけ大口を叩いておいて実際はこの体たらく。\nお前らの「管理」が生ぬるい証ではないのかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01351",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "大口とか、ちょっと分からないんですけど……\nでも、あなたのやり方がおかしいのは分かります！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01352",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "人を管理するとか、そんなのは誰も幸せにならない！\n教え導くのではなく、寄り添うことが必要なんです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01353",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "昔、私に寄り添っていつも優しくしてくれた\nお兄ちゃんのように……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01354",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "寄り添うことは否定しないぞ。ただ、力による「管理」\nが必要だ。各地を旅して、それが分かりかけてきた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01355",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "何か良くないことがあれば、\nそれは私たちが法の下に……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01356",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "そのやり方がぬるかったから、この英雄ヘルト様が\n一肌脱ごうと言っているのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01357",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "こ、こんな圧、ボスの説教に比べたら……！\nあなたは、間違ってます！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01358",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "タイニー……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01359",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺の圧を受けて、下がるどころか前に出るとはな……\nやるじゃないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01360",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺は旅の途中だ。まだ見てない地域もある。\nすべてを見聞するまでは、寛容でいてやろう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01361",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "じゃあな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01362",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "え、えっと、どうしましょう？\n応援を呼んで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01363",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "アルビーナの話からすると数で掛かっても無駄だ。\nそれより今は陛下の手当てを",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01364",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "りょ、了解です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01365",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]